gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAssault class: M16A3/A4 or HK416<br />\nEngineer: SCAR-H<br />\nSniper: M39EMR / M40<br />\nSupport: M60E4<br />\n<br />\nBF4啲槍用落點都差咁啲，HK416 nerf得太多，M60又要比錢"},{"pid":"6333c888b0f86a923452532bd7ebefe3feddd4cb","tid":487203,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"好記得bf3 個airplane mission做得好靚<br />\nBf4 bf1都有玩<br />\n1唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e328513bce9b4c40313538e1137d2da380401f0","tid":487203,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"點解1唔好玩 <br />\n1好多野都整得好靚<br />\n而且好有戰爭feel"},{"pid":"ca7a7566377cd1956b7a5ce62e5dffe13ab29a8a","tid":487203,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pubg 真係唔入流。。根本就係steam個啲萬年alpha game。。</blockquote><br />\nPubg唔入流都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b922877dd811fe1165aa6bdbf3fca0069e759bdc","tid":487203,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Pubg 真係唔入流。。根本就係steam個啲萬年alpha game。。</blockquote><br />\nPubg唔入流都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梗係唔入流啦！<br />\n一隻出色嘅遊戲係潮流興嗰陣都有人玩,例如BF3,CODWaW,Biohazard初代等, 明明係4、5年前甚至咁耐之前嘅遊戲 但係都仲有人玩，咁就係成功<br />\n<br />\n但係PUBG 純粹係一個熱潮, 當佢過咗之後,下場就會變到好似Deceit咁， 完全冇人玩咁濟<br />\n<br />\n唔信你而家上Steam睇下, Red Orchestra2 係幾年前嘅game of the year, 到而家仲有人玩就證明佢真係一隻好嘅遊戲"},{"pid":"4a7ff929d2dc22b969d25ee26ab07313b13e872f","tid":487203,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:58:37.000Z","msg":"而家啲人成日將一隻遊戲嘅成功與否將遊戲玩嘅人數同埋收益作衡量， 已經冇乜人再重視隻遊戲嘅內容設計， 反而成日同電莖及潮流掛鉤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03c99daf121463ad419abd5c63d057b10aee6b0","tid":487203,"uid":15471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Pubg 真係唔入流。。根本就係steam個啲萬年alpha game。。</blockquote><br />\nPubg唔入流都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估多人用黎做stream就叫入流咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹係有話題性咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}